{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Strange Jigsaws is a puzzle game where you solve strange jigsaws. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Solve 50+ strange jigsaws, each with their own surprising way of being solved. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Explore unusual puzzle worlds themed after jigsaws. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Enter the Jigsawverse, maybe. </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">This is a spiritual sequel to my game &quot;20 Small Mazes&quot;. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Notes on puzzle accessibility: </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> The game is color-blind friendly. Any puzzle that uses color as a mechanic has a colorblind mode in the settings. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> The game has accessibility options for hard of hearing or deaf people. Some puzzles use spoken words. There are options for subtitles, as well as full closed captioning of the game (sound effects, background music, etc.). </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Some puzzles require knowledge of English. </p></li></ul>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2702170/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1739384544","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2702170/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1739384544","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2702170/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1739384544","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2702170/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1739384544","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Full controller support","id":28}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"controller_support":"full","detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Strange Jigsaws is a puzzle game where you solve strange jigsaws. </